inspection_note: The home, built in 1983, appears well-maintained with stucco exterior walls. The windows seem original and may benefit from replacement to improve insulation. The roof looks in good condition, but check for insulation in the attic to ensure efficiency. Overall, the property seems to be in good condition with average efficiency features for its age.
